AcceptDataworksEvent.title: AcceptDataworksEvent
AcceptDataworksEvent.summary: Receives and processes system event messages sent by DataWorks.

AddImage.title: AddImage
AddImage.summary: Adds a custom image to a workspace.

AddMemberRole.title: AddMemberRole
AddMemberRole.summary: Adds a role to a member in a workspace. After you add a role to a member, the member is granted the permissions of the role.

ChangeResourceGroup.title: ChangeResourceGroup
ChangeResourceGroup.summary: Changes the resource group to which a resource belongs based on the ID.

CreateCodeSource.title: CreateCodeSource
CreateCodeSource.summary: Creates a code build in Platform for AI (PAI). You can configure Git branches and commit IDs. After the code build is created, you can reference the code build in a Deep Learning Containers (DLC) job.

CreateConnection.title: CreateConnection
CreateConnection.summary: Creates a connection. This API is used to connect Platform for AI (PAI) to customer models and databases in LangStudio and multimodal dataset search scenarios.

CreateDatasetFileMetas.title: CreateDatasetFileMetas
CreateDatasetFileMetas.summary: Creates the metadata records of multiple files in a dataset at a time.

CreateDatasetJobConfig.title: CreateDatasetJobConfig
CreateDatasetJobConfig.summary: Creates a job configuration for a dataset.

CreateDatasetVersionLabels.title: CreateDatasetVersionLabels
CreateDatasetVersionLabels.summary: Creates tags for a dataset version.

CreateMember.title: CreateMember
CreateMember.summary: Adds a user to a workspace as a member. You can add multiple users as members.

CreateModel.title: CreateModel
CreateModel.summary: Creates a model. A model is a collection of model versions. When you create a model, you must specify the model name and description.

CreateModelLabels.title: CreateModelLabels
CreateModelLabels.summary: Creates a tag for a model.

CreateModelVersion.title: CreateModelVersion
CreateModelVersion.summary: Creates a new version for the specified model.

CreateModelVersionLabels.title: CreateModelVersionLabels
CreateModelVersionLabels.summary: Creates a tag for a model version.

CreateProductOrders.title: CreateProductOrders
CreateProductOrders.summary: Creates a pay-as-you-go order for DataWorks, OSS, PAI, or MaxCompute.

CreateRun.title: CreateRun
CreateRun.summary: Creates a run. A run is an experiment that can be associated with a specific workload or simply a code execution.

DeleteCodeSource.title: DeleteCodeSource
DeleteCodeSource.summary: Deletes a code source based on the provided ID.

DeleteDatasetFileMetas.title: DeleteDatasetFileMetas
DeleteDatasetFileMetas.summary: Deletes the metadata records of multiple files in a dataset at a time.

DeleteDatasetJobConfig.title: DeleteDatasetJobConfig
DeleteDatasetJobConfig.summary: Deletes a job configuration for a dataset.

DeleteDatasetVersion.title: DeleteDatasetVersion
DeleteDatasetVersion.summary: Deletes the information about a specified version of a dataset. Version v1 cannot be deleted by using this operation. When you call the DeleteDataset operation to delete a dataset, it can be deleted at the same time.

DeleteMembers.title: DeleteMembers
DeleteMembers.summary: Deletes a member from a workspace.

DeleteModelLabels.title: DeleteModelLabels
DeleteModelLabels.summary: Deletes the labels of a model.

DeleteRunLabel.title: DeleteRunLabel
DeleteRunLabel.summary: Deletes a tag that is added to a run.

DeleteWorkspace.title: DeleteWorkspace
DeleteWorkspace.summary: Deletes a workspace. After you delete a workspace, the associated resources are not automatically released. You must manually release the resources.

DeleteWorkspaceResource.title: DeleteWorkspaceResource
DeleteWorkspaceResource.summary: Deletes a resource from a workspace. The resource is not deleted at the underlying layer.

GetCodeSource.title: GetCodeSource
GetCodeSource.summary: Obtains the details of a code source.

GetDatasetFileMeta.title: GetDatasetFileMeta
GetDatasetFileMeta.summary: Queries the metadata records of specific files in a dataset.

GetDatasetFileMetasStatistics.title: GetDatasetFileMetasStatistics
GetDatasetFileMetasStatistics.summary: Obtains metadata statistics of a dataset.

GetDatasetJobConfig.title: GetDatasetJobConfig
GetDatasetJobConfig.summary: Obtains a job configuration for a dataset.

GetDatasetVersion.title: GetDatasetVersion
GetDatasetVersion.summary: Obtains the information about a specified version of a dataset.

GetDefaultWorkspace.title: GetDefaultWorkspace
GetDefaultWorkspace.summary: Queries information about the default workspace.

GetImage.title: GetImage
GetImage.summary: Obtains the information about an image.

GetMember.title: GetMember
GetMember.summary: Obtains a member in a workspace.

GetModel.title: GetModel
GetModel.summary: Obtains the details of a specified model.

GetWorkspace.title: GetWorkspace
GetWorkspace.summary: Queries the details about a workspace.

ListCodeSources.title: ListCodeSources
ListCodeSources.summary: Lists code sources. Pagination, sorting, and filtering by condition are supported.

ListConfigs.title: ListConfigs
ListConfigs.summary: Obtains a list of workspace configurations.

ListDatasetFileMetas.title: ListDatasetFileMetas
ListDatasetFileMetas.summary: Queries a list of dataset files.

ListDatasetJobConfigs.title: ListDatasetJobConfigs
ListDatasetJobConfigs.summary: Queries the dataset job configurations at a time.

ListDatasets.title: ListDatasets
ListDatasets.summary: Lists the datasets in a workspace.

ListImageLabels.title: ListImageLabels
ListImageLabels.summary: Lists all tags of an image.

ListMembers.title: ListMembers
ListMembers.summary: Obtains the members in a workspace.

ListModelVersions.title: ListModelVersions
ListModelVersions.summary: Queries a list of model versions.

ListPermissions.title: ListPermissions
ListPermissions.summary: Lists the permissions that a user has in a workspace.

ListResources.title: ListResources
ListResources.summary: Queries the resources that are associated with a workspace.

ListRunMetrics.title: ListRunMetrics
ListRunMetrics.summary: Lists the metrics for a run.

ListWorkspaceUsers.title: ListWorkspaceUsers
ListWorkspaceUsers.summary: Lists the users who do not belong to a workspace. These users can be added to the workspace as members.

ListWorkspaces.title: ListWorkspaces
ListWorkspaces.summary: Lists all workspaces in a region.

LogRunMetrics.title: LogRunMetrics
LogRunMetrics.summary: Logs multiple metrics for a run at a time.

PublishCodeSource.title: PublishCodeSource
PublishCodeSource.summary: Publishes a private code source to a workspace to make the code source publicly accessible.

PublishDataset.title: PublishDataset
PublishDataset.summary: Publishes a private dataset in a workspace.

PublishImage.title: PublishImage
PublishImage.summary: Publishes an image. After the image is published, the visibility of the image is changed from PRIVATE to PUBLIC.

UpdateConfig.title: UpdateConfig
UpdateConfig.summary: Updates or adds a workspace configuration item.

UpdateConfigs.title: UpdateConfigs
UpdateConfigs.summary: Updates or adds workspace configurations in batches.

UpdateDataset.title: UpdateDataset
UpdateDataset.summary: Updates the name, description, and other information about a dataset.

UpdateDatasetFileMetas.title: UpdateDatasetFileMetas
UpdateDatasetFileMetas.summary: Updates the metadata records of multiple files in a dataset at a time.

UpdateDatasetJobConfig.title: UpdateDatasetJobConfig
UpdateDatasetJobConfig.summary: Updates a job configuration for a dataset.

UpdateDatasetVersion.title: UpdateDatasetVersion
UpdateDatasetVersion.summary: Updates the information about a specified version of a dataset.

UpdateDefaultWorkspace.title: UpdateDefaultWorkspace
UpdateDefaultWorkspace.summary: Specifies a workspace as the default workspace.

UpdateModel.title: UpdateModel
UpdateModel.summary: Updates the basic configuration information about a model.

UpdateWorkspace.title: UpdateWorkspace
UpdateWorkspace.summary: Updates the name and description of a workspace.

UpdateWorkspaceResource.title: UpdateWorkspaceResource
UpdateWorkspaceResource.summary: Updates the resources of a workspace.
